></div></section><section class=\"border-t py-20 sm:py-28 md:py-32\" style=\"border-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.08)\"><div class=\"relative mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 text-center\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px)\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(12px)\"><span class=\"mb-6 block font-display text-6xl font-bold leading-none sm:text-7xl md:text-8xl\" style=\"color:var(--accent);opacity:0.25\" aria-hidden=\"true\">“</span><blockquote class=\"font-sans text-lg leading-relaxed italic sm:text-xl md:text-2xl\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.75)\">They fixed our outdated website and built us something modern and professional. Since the new site went live, we&#x27;re ranking higher in Google and getting more enquiries and bookings than ever before.</blockquote><div class=\"mt-8\"><p class=\"font-display text-sm font-bold tracking-wide sm:text-base\" style=\"color:var(--accent)\">Sven Haltmann</p><p class=\"mt-1 font-sans text-xs sm:text-sm\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35)\">Aviation Expeditions<!-- --> · <!-- -->Tourism · Alaska</p></div></div><div class=\"mt-10 flex items-center justify-center gap-3\"><button aria-label=\"View testimonial 1\" class=\"transition-all duration-300\" style=\"width:48px;height:4px;border-radius:2px;background:var(--accent);border:none;cursor:pointer\"></button><button aria-label=\"View testimonial 2\" class=\"transition-all duration-300\" style=\"width:32px;height:4px;border-radius:2px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.15);border:none;cursor:pointer\"></button><button aria-label=\"View testimonial 3\" class=\"transition-all duration-300\" style=\"width:32px;height:4px;border-radius:2px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.15);border:none;cursor:pointer\"></button></div><div class=\"mt-6 flex items-center justify-center gap-8\"><button class=\"flex flex-col items-center gap-1.5 border-none bg-transparent transition-opacity duration-300\" style=\"opacity:1;cursor:pointer;padding:8px\" aria-label=\"Testimonial from Sven Haltmann\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center rounded-full font-display text-sm font-bold\" style=\"width:36px;height:36px;background:linear-gradient(135deg, #2ec4b6 0%, #1a8a7f 100%);color:#050505\">SH</div><span class=\"font-display text-[11px]\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5)\">Sven</span></button><button class=\"flex flex-col items-center gap-1.5 border-none bg-transparent transition-opacity duration-300\" style=\"opacity:0.35;cursor:pointer;padding:8px\" aria-label=\"Testimonial from Max Ancic\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center rounded-full font-display text-sm font-bold\" style=\"width:36px;height:36px;background:linear-gradient(135deg, #2ec4b6 0%, #1a8a7f 100%);color:#050505\">MA</div><span class=\"font-display text-[11px]\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5)\">Max</span></button><button class=\"flex flex-col items-center gap-1.5 border-none bg-transparent transition-opacity duration-300\" style=\"opacity:0.35;cursor:pointer;padding:8px\" aria-label=\"Testimonial from Brae Ovens\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center rounded-full font-display text-sm font-bold\" style=\"width:36px;height:36px;background:linear-gradient(135deg, #2ec4b6 0%, #1a8a7f 100%);color:#050505\">BO</div><span class=\"font-display text-[11px]\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5)\">Brae</span></button></div></div></section><section class=\"relative overflow-hidden pt-24 sm:pt-32 md:pt-52\" style=\"background:#0d0d0d;padding-bottom:220px\"><canvas class=\"absolute inset-0 h-full w-full cursor-crosshair\" style=\"-webkit-mask-image:linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent 0%, black 15%, black 55%, transparent 80%);mask-image:linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent 0%, black 15%, black 55%, transparent 80%)\"></canvas><div class=\"pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-0 top-0\" style=\"height:35%;background:linear-gradient(to bottom, #050505 0%, transparent 100%);z-index:1\"></div><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 text-center\" style=\"position:relative;z-index:10;op